you knew Johnny Fontane!

176
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:20,980
-Sure. You want to meet him?
-Great! Sure.

177
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:24,740
-My father helped him with his career.
-He did?

178
00:18:24,860 --> 00:18:25,860
How?

179
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:28,260
