874
01:37:03,220 --> 01:37:05,300
Really put together.

875
01:37:05,380 --> 01:37:06,380
Right, Calo?

876
01:37:06,460 --> 01:37:07,500
(REPEATING IN ITALIAN)

877
01:37:09,980 --> 01:37:11,900
Such hair , such mouth!

878
01:37:14,140 --> 01:37:17,220
The girls around here are
beautiful...but virtuous.

879
01:37:17,740 --> 01:37:20,020
This one had a purple dress...

880
01:37:20,380 --> 01:37:22,420
And a purple ribbon in her hair.

881
01:37:23,260 --> 01:37:26,300
A type more Greek than Italian.

882
01:37:27,220 --> 01:37:28,220
(REPEATING)

883
01:37:28,620 --> 01:37:30,380
Do you know her?

884
01:37:34,620 --> 01:37:37,300
There's no girl like that
in this town.

885
01:37:39,900 --> 01:37:41,060
My God, I understand!

886
01:37:41,180 --> 01:37:43,220
(OWNER SHOUTING IN ITALIAN)

887
01:37:44,980 --> 01:37:45,980
What's wrong?

888
01:37:48,060 --> 01:37:49,420
Let's go.

889
01:37:51,260 --> 01:37:52,500
It's his daughter.

890
01:37:52,940 --> 01:37:54,380
Tell him to come here.

891
01:37:57,620 --> 01:37:58,900
Call him.

892
01:38:09,300 --> 01:38:11,300
(MEN CHATTERING IN ITALIAN)

893
01:38:18,140 --> 01:38:20,380
Fabrizio, you translate.

894
01:38:24,340 --> 01:38:26,020
I apologize if I offended you.

895
01:38:26,100 --> 01:38:27,100
(TRANSLATING IN ITALIAN)

896
01:38:27,180 --> 01:38:30,420
a stranger in this country.

897
01:38:30,500 --> 01:38:33,460
I meant no disrespect
to you or your daughter.

898
01:38:38,700 --> 01:38:41,460
an American, hiding in Sicily.

899
01:38:42,820 --> 01:38:45,020
My name is Michael Corleone.

900
01:38:46,980 --> 01:38:50,940
There are people who'd pay
a lot of money for that information.

901
01:38:53,020 --> 01:38:55,940
But then your daughter
would lose a father

902
01:38:57,460 --> 01:38:59,780
instead of gaining a husband.

903
01:39:07,580 --> 01:39:09,700
I want to meet your daughter.

904
01:39:10,340 --> 01:39:14,740
With your permission, and under
the supervision of your family.

905
01:39:15,380 --> 01:39:16,980
With all respect.

906
01:39:22,780 --> 01:39:26,660
