01:42:21,540 --> 01:42:23,620
SONNY: I'll knock you dizzy.

916
01:42:29,100 --> 01:42:31,140
Save it for the library.

917
01:42:34,660 --> 01:42:37,220
We've got to pick up my sister.

918
01:42:54,500 --> 01:42:56,140
