942
01:48:39,220 --> 01:48:42,900
-I want to reach Michael.
-Nobody knows where he is.

943
01:48:42,980 --> 01:48:45,420
All we know is that he's all right.

944
01:48:47,860 --> 01:48:51,340
-What was that?
-An accident, but nobody was hurt.

945
01:48:52,420 --> 01:48:56,340
